<div class="content">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="event-section padd-top padd-bottom">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-6 set-margin-bot">
                    <div class="about-section">
                        <h2>about us</h2>
                        <div class="common-padd-top about-section-para">
                            <p>
                                Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry.
                                Lorem Ipsum has been the industry's standard dummy text ever since the 1500s,
                                when an unknown printer took
                                a galley of type and scrambled it to make a <strong class="strong">Checkout out video background</strong>
                        </div>
                        <figure class="video-image">
                            <img src="~/assets/images/about-image.jpg" alt="video-image" data-video="https://www.youtube.com/embed/E5ln4uR4TwQ?autoplay=1" />
